title: DSC209R Lab 8: Geospatial Visualization
description: A dynamic visualization of Boston's bike traffic trends using D3.js, Svelte, and Mapbox GL. This project showcases geospatial data, interactive time filtering, and a custom legend for traffic flow representation.
